<abstract>New York Truck Routes, 2026 is a line theme representing the set of roads that commercial vehicles must use in New York City as of 2026. Columbia library staff accessed this data in April of 2026 from the NYC Open Data portal at https://data.cityofnewyork.us/Transportation/New-York-City-Truck-Routes/jjja-shxy/about_data and has provided it in the geopackage format in state plane coordinates. A codebook is included in the full download package.
		</abstract>
		<purpose>To support city agency operational requirements and public data access. </purpose>
	</descript>
